| id | name    | database1      | cur_schema |
+----+---------+----------------+------------+
|  1 | insert1 | duplicate-whh1 | whh1       |
|  2 | insert2 | whh1whh1       | whh1       |
|  3 | 萌萌    | whh3           | whh1       |
|  4 | 萌萌    | whh3           | whh1       |
|  5 | 康康    | whhtest        | whh1       |
|  7 | 洋洋    | whhtest2       | whh1       |
|  8 | 康康    | whhtest        | whh1       |
